Title: WICK TRIMMER
Body (HTML): Keeping your wicks trimmed properly will help your candles burn fully and last longer. Title: WICK DIPPER
Body (HTML): Our wick dipper is used to snuff a candle out while also preventing the wick from continuing to smoke and smolder. Simply hook the wick and dip the flame into the melted wax. The flame extinguishes with no soot or smoke and is now coated in a thin layer of wax. Properly trim the wick and you are ready for your next lighting.åÊ
